column6:
Twin funerals deepen and darken the saga of young Alex Island and his mysterious protector, Omega The Unknown. Also in this issue: Alex goes to college! And we get a glimpse of some genuine panels from the comic-within-a-comic, The Unparalleled Mink, by a special guest artist.,2008,3
Rated T+ ...$2.99
column8: | penciller (cover):Farel Dalrymple | colorist:Paul Hornschemeier | writer:JONATHAN LETHEM KARL RUSNAK
